#: ../../utils/run_utils.rst:3
msgid "Run Utils"
msgstr "Run Utils（執行工具）"

#: ../../utils/run_utils.rst:5
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "目錄"

#: ../../utils/run_utils.rst:8
msgid "ExperimentGrid"
msgstr "ExperimentGrid"

#: ../../utils/run_utils.rst:10
msgid ""
"Spinning Up ships with a tool called ExperimentGrid for making "
"hyperparameter ablations easier. This is based on (but simpler than) `the"
" rllab tool`_ called VariantGenerator."
msgstr ""
"Spinning Up 內建了一個名為 ExperimentGrid 的工具，用於簡化超參數消融實驗"
"（hyperparameter ablation）。這是基於（但比其更簡單的）`the rllab tool`_ 中名為 "
"VariantGenerator 的工具。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid:1
msgid "Tool for running many experiments given hyperparameter ranges."
msgstr "根據超參數範圍執行多組實驗的工具。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.add:1
msgid "Add a parameter (key) to the grid config, with potential values (vals)."
msgstr "將一個參數（key）及其可能的值（vals）加入網格設定中。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.add:3
msgid ""
"By default, if a shorthand isn't given, one is automatically generated "
"from the key using the first three letters of each colon-separated term. "
"To disable this behavior, change ``DEFAULT_SHORTHAND`` in the "
"``spinup/user_config.py`` file to ``False``."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下，如果未提供縮寫，會自動從 key 中每個以冒號分隔的詞彙取前三個字母"
"來產生縮寫。要停用此行為，請將 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 檔案中的 "
"``DEFAULT_SHORTHAND`` 改為 ``False``。"

#: ../../utils/run_utils.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "參數"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.add:8
msgid "Name of parameter."
msgstr "參數名稱。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.add:10
msgid "Allowed values of parameter."
msgstr "參數的允許值。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.add:12
msgid ""
"Optional, shortened name of parameter. For example, maybe the parameter "
"``steps_per_epoch`` is shortened to ``steps``."
msgstr ""
"可選的參數縮寫名稱。例如，參數 ``steps_per_epoch`` 可以縮寫為 ``steps``。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.add:16
msgid ""
"When constructing variant names, force the inclusion of this parameter "
"into the name."
msgstr "在建構變體名稱時，強制將此參數包含在名稱中。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.print:1
msgid "Print a helpful report about the experiment grid."
msgstr "印出關於實驗網格的實用報告。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.run:1
msgid "Run each variant in the grid with function 'thunk'."
msgstr "使用函式 'thunk' 執行網格中的每個變體。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.run:3
msgid ""
"Note: 'thunk' must be either a callable function, or a string. If it is a"
" string, it must be the name of a parameter whose values are all callable"
" functions."
msgstr ""
"注意：'thunk' 必須是可呼叫的函式或字串。如果是字串，它必須是一個參數名稱，"
"且該參數的所有值都必須是可呼叫的函式。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.run:7
msgid ""
"Uses ``call_experiment`` to actually launch each experiment, and gives "
"each variant a name using ``self.variant_name()``."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``call_experiment`` 來實際啟動每個實驗，並透過 ``self.variant_name()`` "
"為每個變體命名。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.run:10
msgid ""
"Maintenance note: the args for ExperimentGrid.run should track closely to"
" the args for call_experiment. However, ``seed`` is omitted because we "
"presume the user may add it as a parameter in the grid."
msgstr ""
"維護說明：ExperimentGrid.run 的引數應與 call_experiment 的引數密切對應。"
"但 ``seed`` 被省略了，因為我們假設使用者可能會將它作為網格中的參數來添加。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variant_name:1
msgid "Given a variant (dict of valid param/value pairs), make an exp_name."
msgstr "根據一個變體（有效的參數／值對組成的 dict），產生 exp_name。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variant_name:3
msgid ""
"A variant's name is constructed as the grid name (if you've given it "
"one), plus param names (or shorthands if available) and values separated "
"by underscores."
msgstr ""
"變體的名稱由網格名稱（如果有指定的話）加上參數名稱（或可用的縮寫）和值組成，"
"以底線分隔。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variant_name:7
msgid "Note: if ``seed`` is a parameter, it is not included in the name."
msgstr "注意：如果 ``seed`` 是參數之一，它不會被包含在名稱中。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:1
msgid "Makes a list of dicts, where each dict is a valid config in the grid."
msgstr "產生一個 dict 的列表，其中每個 dict 是網格中的一個有效設定。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:3
msgid "There is special handling for variant parameters whose names take the form"
msgstr "對於名稱採用以下形式的變體參數，有特殊的處理方式"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:6
msgid "``'full:param:name'``."
msgstr "``'full:param:name'``。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:8
msgid ""
"The colons are taken to indicate that these parameters should have a "
"nested dict structure. eg, if there are two params,"
msgstr ""
"冒號被視為表示這些參數應具有巢狀的 dict 結構。例如，如果有兩個參數，"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:12
msgid "Key"
msgstr "鍵"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:12
msgid "Val"
msgstr "值"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:14
msgid "``'base:param:a'``"
msgstr "``'base:param:a'``"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:14
msgid "1"
msgstr "1"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:15
msgid "``'base:param:b'``"
msgstr "``'base:param:b'``"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:15
msgid "2"
msgstr "2"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.ExperimentGrid.variants:18
msgid "the variant dict will have the structure"
msgstr "則變體 dict 將具有以下結構"

#: ../../utils/run_utils.rst:19
msgid "Calling Experiments"
msgstr "呼叫實驗"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:1
msgid "Run a function (thunk) with hyperparameters (kwargs), plus configuration."
msgstr "使用超參數（kwargs）和設定來執行一個函式（thunk）。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:3
msgid ""
"This wraps a few pieces of functionality which are useful when you want "
"to run many experiments in sequence, including logger configuration and "
"splitting into multiple processes for MPI."
msgstr ""
"這封裝了一些在你想要依序執行多個實驗時很有用的功能，包括 logger 設定和為 "
"MPI 分割成多個程序。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:7
msgid ""
"There's also a SpinningUp-specific convenience added into executing the "
"thunk: if ``env_name`` is one of the kwargs passed to call_experiment, "
"it's assumed that the thunk accepts an argument called ``env_fn``, and "
"that the ``env_fn`` should make a gym environment with the given "
"``env_name``."
msgstr ""
"在執行 thunk 時還加入了 Spinning Up 特有的便利功能：如果 ``env_name`` 是傳給 "
"call_experiment 的 kwargs 之一，則假設 thunk 接受一個名為 ``env_fn`` 的引數，"
"且 ``env_fn`` 應使用給定的 ``env_name`` 建立一個 gym 環境。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:12
msgid ""
"The way the experiment is actually executed is slightly complicated: the "
"function is serialized to a string, and then ``run_entrypoint.py`` is "
"executed in a subprocess call with the serialized string as an argument. "
"``run_entrypoint.py`` unserializes the function call and executes it. We "
"choose to do it this way---instead of just calling the function directly "
"here---to avoid leaking state between successive experiments."
msgstr ""
"實驗的實際執行方式稍微複雜一些：函式會被序列化為字串，然後在子程序中以序列化的"
"字串作為引數執行 ``run_entrypoint.py``。``run_entrypoint.py`` 會反序列化函式"
"呼叫並執行它。我們選擇這種方式——而不是直接在此處呼叫函式——是為了避免連續實驗"
"之間的狀態洩漏。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:19
#: spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:24
msgid "Name for experiment."
msgstr "實驗名稱。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:21
msgid "A python function."
msgstr "一個 Python 函式。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:23
msgid "Seed for random number generators."
msgstr "隨機數產生器的種子。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:25
msgid ""
"Number of MPI processes to split into. Also accepts 'auto', which will "
"set up as many procs as there are cpus on the machine."
msgstr ""
"要分割成的 MPI 程序數量。也接受 'auto'，這會設定與機器上 CPU 數量相同的程序數。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:29
msgid ""
"Used in configuring the logger, to decide where to store experiment "
"results. Note: if left as None, data_dir will default to "
"``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR`` from ``spinup/user_config.py``."
msgstr ""
"用於設定 logger，以決定實驗結果的儲存位置。注意：如果保留為 None，data_dir "
"將預設為 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中的 ``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR``。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.call_experiment:33
msgid "All kwargs to pass to thunk."
msgstr "傳給 thunk 的所有 kwargs。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:1
msgid "Sets up the output_dir for a logger and returns a dict for logger kwargs."
msgstr "為 logger 設定 output_dir 並回傳一個包含 logger kwargs 的 dict。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:3
msgid "If no seed is given and datestamp is false,"
msgstr "如果未提供 seed 且 datestamp 為 false，"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:9
msgid "If a seed is given and datestamp is false,"
msgstr "如果提供了 seed 且 datestamp 為 false，"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:15
msgid "If datestamp is true, amend to"
msgstr "如果 datestamp 為 true，則修改為"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:21
msgid ""
"You can force datestamp=True by setting ``FORCE_DATESTAMP=True`` in "
"``spinup/user_config.py``."
msgstr ""
"你可以在 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中設定 ``FORCE_DATESTAMP=True`` 來強制啟用 "
"datestamp=True。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:26
msgid "Seed for random number generators used by experiment."
msgstr "實驗所使用的隨機數產生器的種子。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:28
msgid ""
"Path to folder where results should be saved. Default is the "
"``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR`` in ``spinup/user_config.py``."
msgstr ""
"結果儲存資料夾的路徑。預設為 ``spinup/user_config.py`` 中的 "
"``DEFAULT_DATA_DIR``。"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:31
msgid "Whether to include a date and timestamp in the name of the save directory."
msgstr "是否在儲存目錄的名稱中包含日期和時間戳記。"

#: ../../utils/run_utils.rst
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "回傳值"

#: of spinup.utils.run_utils.setup_logger_kwargs:35
msgid "logger_kwargs, a dict containing output_dir and exp_name."
msgstr "logger_kwargs，一個包含 output_dir 和 exp_name 的 dict。"
